    <p>ARI­ZONA ZERVAS</p>
    <p>Song: Rox­anne Watch it at: bit.ly/2YkLAiO</p>
    <p>Amer­i­can singer and rap­per Ari­zona Zervas (above) had re­leased al­most 30 sin­gles since 2016 be­fore fi­nally scor­ing a hit with Rox­anne.</p>
    <p>The song, not to be con­fused with the 1978 clas­sic by Sting’s old band The Po­lice, stayed in the Top 10 of Bill­board’s pop charts from De­cem­ber last year to April this year.</p>
    <p>Re­leased in Oc­to­ber last year, the song was used in hun­dreds of thou­sands of Tik­Tok videos within a week.</p>
    <p>The catchy tune went on to sound­track mil­lions of Tik­Tok videos rang­ing from make-up tu­to­ri­als to dance moves.</p>
    <p>Af­ter it be­came a main­stream hit, it topped the charts in New Zealand and was also in the Top 10 in coun­tries such as Bri­tain, Aus­tralia and Singapore.</p>

